l:dependency.name: Generic Webhook Trigger Plugin
l:dependency.l:description: Can receive any HTTP request, extract any values from JSON or XML and trigger a job with those values available as variables. Works with GitHub, GitLab, Bitbucket, Jira and many more.

l:dependency.name: commons-ip-math
l:dependency.l:description: A project to make it easier to work with Internet resources, such as IPv4, IPv6 and AS numbers.

l:dependency.name: OWASP Java HTML Sanitizer
l:dependency.l:description: Takes third-party HTML and produces HTML that is safe to embed in your web application. Fast and easy to configure.

l:dependency.name: Java 10 Shim
l:dependency.l:description: Provides an implementation of java8-shim that interoperates with Java >= 10 idioms for immutable collections.

l:dependency.name: Java 8 Shim
l:dependency.l:description: Backports @since Java 9 collection factories like List.of onto Java8 in a way that uses the real ones where available, falls back to a conforming implementation on Java8 and JIT compiles well.
